title: Terra Obscura v1-2 (2003-2005) (Complete) (digital) (Tithe-Empir
description:
English | CBR | 12 Issues

Terra Obscura v1 #1-6 and Terra Obscura v2 #1-6
Publisher:  America's Best Comics
Publication Date:  August 2003 - February 2004 and October 2004 - May 2005

Writer:  Alan Moore and Peter Hogan
Penciler:  Yanick Paquette
Inkers (v1):  Karl Story (#1-6), John Dell (#6), Jimmy Palmiotti (#6), and Richard Friend (#6)
Inkers (v2):  Karl Story (#1-6), Ray Snyder (#5-6), and Serge LaPoint (#5-6)
Colorists (v1):  Jeromy Cox (#1-6) and Tony Avina (#6)
Colorists (v2):  Carrie Strachan (#1-3), Mike Komai (#4), and Joel Benjamin (#5-6)
Letterer:  Todd Klein

Spinning out of TOM STRONG, the heroes of the Society of Major American Science Heroes have returned after 30 years in suspended animation! Can they adjust to life in a brave new world and band together to take on a threat seeking to overthrow the western United States?

Thanks goes to Tithe for this release.
